snippet.textDisplay: Talking about time moving fast: I remember I started watching you a year or two before you began your daily vlogs. A year after you started vlogging I moved to New York City, and I remember running into you and telling you I just moved here. You gave me a hug and told me how exciting it is & welcomed me. Now, more than 4 years later, I relocated to The Netherlands, my 4 years NYC chapter being a crazy adventure. All in all, this is to say that I've been watching you before you even had your first million, before the vlogs, before 368, and I'm honored to have seen this whole journey. Very grateful that I was able to run into you too :)
